    "description": "当表面的和平再也无法维持的时候，曾经最平静的国度爆发了战争。而今，昔日的避风港变成了末日废墟。法律与规则不复存在，唯有强者才能生存下来。安全没了保障，恐惧笼罩着每个人。想活下来，保护你所爱的人，要付出什么代价？你之后就会知道了……<br><br><br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370280/extras/3d6501d7402a9bffda79260614dd419f.poster.avif?t=1747218077\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370280/extras/3d6501d7402a9bffda79260614dd419f.webm?t=1747218077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370280/extras/3d6501d7402a9bffda79260614dd419f.mp4?t=1747218077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>跟踪者？</strong><br>在《Nobody's Left》中，你有时候会遭到敌人的偷袭。他们发现你之后，会躲起来等待合适的时机袭击你！所以要小心，别太着急。<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370280/extras/ef59694f0cea8ecabaa1fb10fca92676.poster.avif?t=1747218077\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370280/extras/ef59694f0cea8ecabaa1fb10fca92676.webm?t=1747218077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370280/extras/ef59694f0cea8ecabaa1fb10fca92676.mp4?t=1747218077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>潜行任务</strong><br>有时候难免遇到敌众我寡的情况，这时你就必须运用你的潜行技能来击败敌人。千万把脚步放轻，因为一旦弄出声响，等待着你的很可能就是死亡的命运。<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370280/extras/914131cd2c429ff269769d20f86809f2.poster.avif?t=1747218077\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370280/extras/914131cd2c429ff269769d20f86809f2.webm?t=1747218077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370280/extras/914131cd2c429ff269769d20f86809f2.mp4?t=1747218077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>独特的背景叙事</strong><br>试着找找任务里的彩蛋吧。每个彩蛋都包含一个关于游戏背景的故事，可以帮助你更全面地了解游戏的世界观，补充游戏剧情。<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370280/extras/6cc3ea8795df09c0277b956aa2d73bd4.poster.avif?t=1747218077\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370280/extras/6cc3ea8795df09c0277b956aa2d73bd4.webm?t=1747218077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370280/extras/6cc3ea8795df09c0277b956aa2d73bd4.mp4?t=1747218077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>近身战斗</strong><br>当你不幸败下阵来，双眼正要缓缓阖上，然而我们顶尖质量的游戏音乐会让你的血液再次沸腾。如果你不放弃，仍然还有活下去的机会！<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370280/extras/cb9560b767e3f691d05f6a2de8be74c3.poster.avif?t=1747218077\" width=600 height=240 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370280/extras/cb9560b767e3f691d05f6a2de8be74c3.webm?t=1747218077\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2370280/extras/cb9560b767e3f691d05f6a2de8be74c3.mp4?t=1747218077\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><strong>武装复仇</strong><br>真实的枪械机制，没有瞄准辅助。你的射击技巧决定了一切。若你的对手也是个神枪手，那就比他先出手吧。",
